	$sketch: ChangeLog,v 1.1 2003/03/04 19:03:46 sketch Exp $

2003-03-04  Jonathan Perkin  <jonathan@perkin.org.uk>

  * Version 0.1

  * API now supports talker and IRC clients, with some basic functionality
    needed to connect and stay on, along with some almost-complete message
    parsers.  Messages are security checked against sane string matches.

  * Add README/COPYRIGHT/install.rb files useful for a tarball.

  * Add this file to track changes.

  * Tag natter-0-1
